==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Disworship
<hw>Dis*wor"ship</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A deprivation of honor; a
cause of disgrace; a discredit.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Disworth</ent>⟦br⟧
